{"type": "article", "id": 12688, "title": "多功能滑板架", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-28T07:28:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122501cCVpd1Rekgi0obIP.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t看完了滑板我们再来看一个滑板架子。这其实一个多功能的墙壁托架，除了普通的托架功能以外，它最大的特色是可以悬挂滑板。设计师在两层架子的一侧开了两个长条状的洞，与墙壁有一定的距离，可以保证滑板挂上去而不会弄脏墙壁。此外，洞洞的大小设计得正好可以作为开瓶器使用，感觉设计师也是为爱喝酒的滑板少男少女们操碎了心。这是<a href=\"http://www.zanocchistarke.com/wall-ride/#itemId=547221a4e4b0530d078880a9\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。这是<a href=\"http://www.zanocchistarke.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的主页</a>，可以查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261404230zcjGdPes3BrfLF6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140423sporOiPkSd0v4RlJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140424CofKWUkxPs1uAEin.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140424yFWs8xX7rDa9e36L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140425r0oRvQ7qkjzwMPdK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140425XPLCMGE7gBwnv1Ul.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.364\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}